trans-unit.source: Initializes the associated <xref:System.ServiceModel.Activities.CorrelationInitializer.CorrelationHandle*> with a callback correlation.
A callback correlation is based on the callback context exchange mechanism described in the [.NET Context Exchange Protocol Specification](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=163882).
trans-unit.target: En tilbakeringing korrelasjon er basert på tilbakeringing konteksten exchange mekanisme som beskrives i den [.NET konteksten Exchange protokoll spesifikasjon](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=163882).

trans-unit.source: To use callback correlation, a context-based binding such as <xref:System.ServiceModel.BasicHttpContextBinding>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.WSHttpContextBinding>, or <xref:System.ServiceModel.NetTcpContextBinding> must be used.
trans-unit.target: Bruke tilbakeringing Korrelasjons en konteksten kodebasert binding som <xref:System.ServiceModel.BasicHttpContextBinding>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.WSHttpContextBinding>, eller <xref:System.ServiceModel.NetTcpContextBinding>må brukes.</xref:System.ServiceModel.NetTcpContextBinding> </xref:System.ServiceModel.WSHttpContextBinding> </xref:System.ServiceModel.BasicHttpContextBinding>
